      "rationale": "Five operating points (2–6 L/min, 2000–3500 rpm) matched to FDA experimental dataset. Fluid viscosity set to 0.0035 Pa·s (glycerol-water blood analog). Inlet velocity profiles derived from PIV measurements. All boundary conditions within ±3% of experimental values. Gradation 2 met."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
